  "description": {
   "en": "Based on \"Rennyo Shonin Go-eden\", it is a manga work that depicts the life of Rennyo Shonin in an easy-to-understand manner. Rennyo (1415-1499) was a monk in the Muromachi period and the founder of Honganji restoration. He is a Jodo Shinshu sect who recites Namo Amida Butsu. Although it is based on historical facts, it also introduces all the legends such as fleshy masks in the Go-eden in a fun way. Since there is not much room on the page, the content is tightly packed. A newly drawn book in 1997"
  },
